title: TOP CHARTS OF THE DAY FOR 5/24/23 – EEIQ, NNTX, NVDA, RRGB
description: 2023/05/24 – Wednesday Top Charts of the Day by Harry Boxer, TheTechTrader.com.EpicQuest Education Group International Limited (EEIQ) made an explosive move on Wednesday, jumping from 1.74 to 3.36, pretty much doubling, backed off and closed up 91 cents, or 62%, to 2.37, on a huge 32.2 million shares traded. I’m looking for this stock to possibly extend. The overall chart pattern shows that after being up in the 8-range for a while, came down to under a dollar, bounced, and at this point it is at resistance. Keep an eye on this stock going forward because if it gets through this zone, you may very well see a 6 to 8-dollar stock.Nutanix, Inc. (NTNX) exploded after hours on strong earnings on Wednesday. I am featuring this here right now because, knowing this company very well, I think this has got to be a trigger. It is coming out of a 6-month falling wedge that takes it up through 30, into the 33-34 zone, and eventually 39-40.NVIDIA Corporation (NVDA) had one of the biggest days of the year on Wednesday for any stock. The low during the session was 298.06, at four o’clock it was 305.41, then in after-hours it exploded to just under 400 to 394.75. A long coil has developed, which leads me to think we should watch this on Thursday for a follow-through day, maybe to 405-410.Red Robin Gourmet Burgers, Inc. (RRGB) has been in an uptrend since January of this year when it was trading around 5.35. On Wednesday it jumped 1.25, or 9%, to 15.22, on 784.5K shares traded and tagged 16.75 in after-hours. I’m looking for a move that gets it to 18 and 21.Other stocks on the long side include Applied Digital Corporation (APLD), Enveric Biosciences, Inc. (ENVB), GigaCloud Technology Inc.
